data.title: Hit of miss but great when they are on
data.text: We order from here now and again and it's pretty good. As far as wings go, this spot is up there in the top few in the area when they focus on quality and consistency. The biggest problem we ever have is them serving the wings soggy and sopping wet with sauce. Sure, you can order them that way, but we always order "well done" to get them crispy. Sometimes it works, sometimes it doesn't (50/50). Friendly staff, best to order for carry out as the inside is a bit small.
